  <thingsToDo><![CDATA[<ul>
<li><strong>Local Onsens</strong> - our hotels have their own onsens but for any guest looking for an authentic, Japanese onsen Hakuba is home to 3 public paths which can be paid for locally</li>
<li><strong>Zenkoji Temple</strong> -  Located in Nagano, any guest taking the bullet train can visit this temple on their way</li>
<li><strong>Matsumoto Castle</strong> - Another site to see in Nagano if you have the time, Matsumoto Castle is one of Japan's historical landmarks. </li>
</ul>]]></thingsToDo>
