  <travelInformation><![CDATA[<p><strong>Travel and Transfer info</strong> – Tokyo 4hrs. Option to upgrade to Bullet Train 3 3/4hrs.</p>
<p>Inghams guests travelling to Japan will receive a Meet &amp; Greet service at Tokyo airport. The local English speaking Guide will ensure you reach your transfer and will be contactable 24/7 via phone throughout your stay.</p>
<p>You will meet your Guide again on your return to Tokyo or Kyoto when they see you off onto your transfer back to the airport.</p>
<p><strong>A local Ski Bus</strong> picks up from outside both our hotels and connects with at least 3 of the Hakuba resorts (alternatively, change at the main bus station).</p>]]></travelInformation>
